title: John FetterTrend 8/15: Dr. Oz. 14 FBI, Passports, Georgia, Capri Sun, Soup

description:
In this edition of John FetterTrend, Jack and Miles discuss Dr. Oz's John Fetterman attack ad, Jim Jordan's 14 FBI whistleblowers, Trump's passports getting seized, the investigation into Rudy Giuliani in Georgia, the Capri Sun recall, and their favorite soups!
